      <Content m="2015-08-27T06:20:27.652683Z">&lt;P&gt;You can reorder the columns at run time. To move the column,&amp;nbsp;drag&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;drop&amp;nbsp;it&amp;nbsp;at the&amp;nbsp;new location. By default the property is set as true.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;IMG border=0 alt="" src="images/reordering.png"&gt; 
&lt;P&gt;To allow&amp;nbsp;reordering of columns, use &lt;STRONG&gt;allowColumnReorder&lt;/STRONG&gt; property:&lt;/P&gt;&lt;innovasys:widget type="Colorized Example Code" layout="block"&gt;&lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="inline" name="Title"&gt;JavaScript&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt; &lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="inline" name="LanguageName"&gt;JS&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt; &lt;innovasys:widgetproperty layout="block" name="Content"&gt;allowColumnReorder: true&lt;/innovasys:widgetproperty&gt;&lt;/innovasys:widget&gt;</Content>
